OL,3,CWoman who drank 'five pints' before
OL,4,Ckilling cyclist has been jailed
OL,6,FA woman who drank "five pints" at the
OL,7,Fpub before killing a cyclist in
OL,8,FSunderland has been jailed.
OL,10,FAli Reza Ghaisar, 48, died following
OL,11,Fthe collision on Hylton Road shortly
OL,12,Fafter 1:20am on 31 July 2022.
OL,14,FMr Ghaisar, who was out cycling at the
OL,15,Ftime, was struck by a blue BMW car,
OL,16,Fwhich then fled the area.
OL,18,FHe was later pronounced dead at the
OL,19,Fscene.
