OL,3,CWoman who drank 'five pints' before
OL,4,Ckilling cyclist has been jailed
OL,6,FFollowing his death, his family
OL,7,Freleased moving tributes to him,
OL,8,Fdescribing him as "one of a kind."
OL,10,FOfficers launched an investigation and
OL,11,Flater identified the driver of the BMW
OL,12,Fvehicle as Vicky Hardy.
OL,14,FShe had left the scene of the
OL,15,Fcollision before later returning.
OL,17,FThe investigation found that on the
OL,18,Fevening of the collision, Hardy had
OL,19,Fdrank five pints of cider in a nearby
OL,20,Fpub before getting behind the wheel.
