OL,3,CWoman who drank 'five pints' before
OL,4,Ckilling cyclist has been jailed
OL,6,FHardy, 44, of Helmsdale Road in
OL,7,FSunderland, was subsequently charged
OL,8,Fwith causing death by dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving.
OL,11,FIn a hearing at Newcastle Crown Court
OL,12,Fin June 2024, Hardy pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fthe offence and was released on
OL,14,Fconditional bail.
OL,16,FHardy was sentenced on 2 September to
OL,17,Fsix years in prison. She was also
OL,18,Fhanded an eight-year driving ban.
