OL,3,CWoman who drank 'five pints' before
OL,4,Ckilling cyclist has been jailed
OL,6,F"This a tragic case, and one which was
OL,7,Fentirely avoidable," Sergeant John
OL,8,FSanderson of Northumbria Police's
OL,9,FSerious Collision Investigation Unit
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"Ali was simply riding his bike at the
OL,13,Ftime when he was struck by Hardy's
OL,14,Fvehicle.
OL,16,F"She then showed a total disregard for
OL,17,Fthe welfare of Ali by fleeing the
OL,18,Fscene and failing to call an ambulance
OL,19,Fand other emergency services.
